data.description: This gorgeous home in South Salina has been recently updated with all new flooring, appliances, paint, and so much more! Walk into a spacious living room on the main level that leads to the dining room and is open to the kitchen! Off of the dining room, you are met with French doors with a great sized fenced in yard. It also offers a concrete patio for grilling and entertaining! Off of the kitchen, you will find the over-sized two car garage that is spacious for all of your activities and vehicles. Going to the upstairs level, you are met with two sizable bedrooms and a large bathroom with a gorgeous double vanity. The main bedroom has a large closet and beautiful windows for awesome natural lighting. Going into the lower level, you will find a very large second living area with an additional bathroom and laundry room combo. On the other side, there is a bonus room that would be perfect for a den, office, or even storage! Don't miss your opportunity to see this phenome home!
